{"tid":688261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心，八十後又開始將自己既失敗歸咎00後","createTime":"2018-06-03T05:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T07:15:06.000Z","uid":149494,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5605765674f843fe330ed470d6ca6edfab9adb42","tid":688261,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"一班永遠得個講字，乜都無做過等運到<br />\n隨住年紀漸大開始慢慢向現實妥協<br />\n演變成為佢地以前口中廢中、廢老既人<br />\n好容易會將社會一切唔順佢地眼既事，推哂比其他人/其他世代"},{"pid":"3c08ac47bfafc9208c8108daf715fc7c73b5ccac","tid":688261,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"根本好多00後一出世就面對中共殖民同洗腦<br />\n好多野佢地都無得揀,都係佢地上一代(即係八十後都有份)，質比佢地食<br />\n就好似班大陸人咁，你唔會期望佢地識對個政權同個社會有批判思考<br />\n反而果班自以為睇得好清既上一代，乜都無做過就將個波係咁射哂比下一代<br />\n同佢地成日鬧既果d廢老有咩分別"},{"pid":"b4db0f08bac812879538659b8cb81625c7267ae6","tid":688261,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"又係呢d論文"},{"pid":"a7dd093c8cbe59f8076c3a1e5a8a2be4306b309f","tid":688261,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"分化00後似乎係新任務喎"},{"pid":"82df3c42ecde9406a377e6950cbdc9f6fc03f5a8","tid":688261,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7dd093c8cbe59f8076c3a1e5a8a2be4306b309f","tid":688261,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"分化00後似乎係新任務喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"未分化都有大代溝，好難搞"},{"pid":"9cd084aa82aa56c4f6bde7eb9bcc3338f4fe0d32","tid":688261,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚玩分化啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申80後從來唔睇年齡屌人<br />\n有開明嘅老人家<br />\n亦有出眾嘅00後</span>"},{"pid":"fb85696cc638f4f95e068bdc56482f3737525879","tid":688261,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cd084aa82aa56c4f6bd